commit.message:
Remove hardcoded 1000 count for BaseApi._iterate

Remove hardcoded count of 1000 and set default count to 500.
This value was chosen because it was suggested by Mailchimp API
support to avoid 504 - Gateway timeout errors. See pr #207.
